By using DigiCap (the “Bot”), you agree to these Terms of Service and our Privacy Policy.
If you do not agree, you must stop using the Bot immediately.

2. Description of Service

DigiCap is a multipurpose Discord bot designed to provide entertainment, economy systems, and automated responses.
The Bot may update, add, or remove features at any time without notice.

3. User Responsibilities

By using DigiCap, you agree:

Not to abuse or exploit the Bot’s features.

Not to use the Bot for spam, harassment, or illegal activities.

Not to attempt to modify, reverse-engineer, or redistribute the Bot’s code.

To follow all applicable laws and Discord’s Terms of Service
.

4. Data Collection and Storage

The Bot may store limited user data such as:

Discord user IDs

Currency balances, daily/work timers, or progress

Command usage logs (for debugging or moderation)

No personal identifying information (like email or passwords) is collected.
All stored data stays within the Bot’s private database and is not shared with third parties.

